{"tid":574523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港女回應】網民質疑賣肉買樓 登台港女：我冇賣身","createTime":"2018-02-27T12:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T12:50:36.000Z","uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9dce1805c2b0f1837ab077d462502097024ada","tid":574523,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180227/2_573467_0/-港女回應-網民質疑賣肉買樓-登台港女-我冇賣身-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F2_573467_0%2F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%B3%A3%E8%82%89%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3-%E6%88%91%E5%86%87%E8%B3%A3%E8%BA%AB-&d=pEr3Gf3csFW2%2FMgE8lB5IKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7be51b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F2_573467_0%2F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%B3%A3%E8%82%89%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3-%E6%88%91%E5%86%87%E8%B3%A3%E8%BA%AB-&h=7750b54f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180227/2_573467_0/-港女回應-網民質疑賣肉買樓-登台港女-我冇賣身-</a><br />\n<br />\n網民說你賣身，有何回應？「可能因為他們沒有看內文，很多人會斷章取義，只是輕輕看看標題，就會質疑我為何花兩年時間登台，就可賺到這筆錢來買樓。但事實是我一直有儲蓄習慣，其實我已不小了，都做了十多年工作(讀書已開始做兼職)，其實儲了些錢也很正常。」 <br />\n<br />\n她又說，自己一直努力工作儲錢，「其實我以前連保安也做過，畢業之後考過保安牌做過保安，之後做過市場推廣，因為大學時讀市場學，之後又轉型全職做模特兒，在街上派小册子又做過。之後再轉型做司儀。」她說自己日常生活十分節儉，連旅行也很少去。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/204333_b208c2963184d6b206679d1dc22e0125.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F204333_b208c2963184d6b206679d1dc22e0125.png&h=340cc035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOphelia希望，網民不要戴有色眼鏡看她們。"},{"pid":"3c16ce691432332bcffd5b6d0653e49e16baa58a","tid":574523,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"算吧啦"},{"pid":"8858dd3d3debdb65d0a89729b6cec0843d9bece2","tid":574523,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"照下鏡先"},{"pid":"98e19932c598ea8feca75ef35d3a960ef9fbebe7","tid":574523,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"冇人信"},{"pid":"a130838a17974c2191b2a9d26451542c0ebac1c9","tid":574523,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:50:36.000Z","msg":"會窮"}]}